@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title NDP (IPv6): NS/NA + RS/RA (concept)

[IPv6 Host] as H
[IPv6 Router] as R
[Other host] as H2

H --> R : RS (Router Solicitation)
R --> H : RA (Router Advertisement)\nprefix, gateway, flags

H -[#333333,dashed]-> H2 : NS (Neighbour Solicitation)\n(to multicast)
H2 -[#333333,dashed]-> H : NA (Neighbour Advertisement)

note bottom
  NDP uses ICMPv6.
  It replaces ARP and part of autoconfiguration.
end note
@enduml
